messages.text:
I found <https://www.zdyn.net/system/hacks/2020/09/19/vscode-term-session.html|this blog post about> enabling the integrated terminal to use tmux for persistent remote sessions - is there something similar that could be done for starting the julia REPL?

```{
  "terminal.integrated.shell.linux": "/usr/bin/tmux",
  "terminal.integrated.shellArgs.linux": [
    "new-session",
    "-A",
    "-s",
    "main"
  ],
}```

